metadata.description:
Playtesting build for Toybox!

Report any bugs found on [url=https://github.com/spoopster/the-toybox]the GitHub repository[/url], and have fun!

So far the mod has:
- 3 playable characters: Atlas, Milcom and Jonas;
	- Atlas and Jonas have a full* set of unlocks, Milcom's unlocks are not added yet (though some of them are in the mod, just unlocked by default)
- 82 findable items, and a few more you can only access by snooping in the files;
- 16 trinkets;
- 2 new (unlockable) cards, 16 new (unlockable) pill effects, 9 new (unlockable) objects;
[strike]- It makes Hell blue;[/strike]
